<body ><div id="Section 1" class="mktEditable" ><div class="WordSection1">&nbsp;<img src="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/honeywell_emailheader_logo.png" alt="" width="140" height="50" /></div>
<div class="WordSection1"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte.Ltd.</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br />2 Loyang Crescent</span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br />508976 Singapore</span></div>
<div class="WordSection1">
<p><span style="color: black; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">August 27, 2015<br /> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p>
<p><span style="color: black; font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Dear Honeywell Customer, </span></p>
<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">As we shared last month, we are entering the final phase of our transition at the Singapore Loyang R&amp;O site. On 27th September 2015, the business activities will transition to the Honeywell International S&agrave;rl (HIS) legal entity. <br /></span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Here&rsquo;s some important information you&rsquo;ll need to know before the changeover: <br /></span><br />
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Your authorized supplier list should reflect the legal entity/name change &ndash; <strong>Honeywell International S&agrave;rl</strong>. Singapore Loyang repair orders need to reference the HIS legal entity starting on 27th September 2015.</span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Your internal financial systems should reflect the legal entity name change &ndash; <strong>Honeywell International S&agrave;rl</strong>. A <a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/Singapore CGM 30 Day Checklist.pdf" target="_blank">transition checklist</a> is available and includes the new supplier address, amended &ldquo;Ship To&rdquo; address, and invoicing and payment bank details. </span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd. (&ldquo;HASPL&rdquo;) will automatically transfer obligations for all open orders in backlog as of 27th September 2015 from HASPL to Honeywell International S&agrave;rl (&ldquo;HIS&rdquo;) and assign all rights and benefits from HASPL to HIS. </span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">With the exception of Contract customers, the HIS default currency is U.S. Dollars for all quotes and invoices.</span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">For Contract Customers only: To avoid any delays in service, please verify your amendment agreements are executed. Our Contract Managers are available to help you to finalize the agreements. </span></li>
</ul>
<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">We have learned from past experience that the best way to minimize order disruptions during the system changeover is for us to designate one week without R&amp;O shipment or R&amp;O incoming order activity. <br /></span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Therefore, we would like to share the dates and details on how this could affect your orders: <br /></span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Saturday, September 26 (5pm SGT</strong>) </span><br />
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">The Singapore Loyang Avionics R&amp;O site will begin transitioning to the enhanced version of SAP. </span></li>
</ul>
<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Saturday, September 26 (5pm SGT) &ndash; Wednesday, September 30 (5pm SGT)</strong> </span><br />
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Honeywell will be unable to process new or existing R&amp;O orders or product shipments between these dates. Orders received during this time period will be placed in a queue for processing on October 1.</span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Orders received before and after this changeover may experience up to one week turnaround delay. <br /><br /></span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">The estimated ship date field in the <a href="http://www.myaerospace.com" target="_blank">MyAerospace.com</a> customer portal will not operate during this time frame, and will not reflect updated shipping data until the changeover is completed on September 30.</span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Any outbound product shipments will be suspended until after the changeover is completed. We may contact you to arrange an early shipment if your requested delivery date falls within the one week changeover period. </span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">For any Aircraft on Ground (AOG) issues during this week, please contact the Honeywell AOG Team at +1-800-601-3099 (US/Canada) or +1-602-365-3099 (International), select phone option #4.</span></li>
</ul>
<strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">October 1 (8am SGT)</span></strong><br />
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Product shipments and new orders will resume at the Singapore Loyang Avionics R&amp;O site using Honeywell International S&agrave;rl (HIS) as the supplier.</span></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">The system upgrade will convert all existing Honeywell sales orders over to new Honeywell numbers. You will need to use your original purchase order number(s) to locate the new sales order number(s) in the <a href="http://www.myaerospace.com" target="_blank">MyAerospace.com </a>customer portal. </span></li>
</ul>
<span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">If you have any questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to contact us via your Honeywell Customer Business Manager, your regular Honeywell representative at the Honeywell Aerospace Singapore Pte. Ltd. (Avionics Loyang) site or send us an email to <a href="mailto:aerocpscommunications@honeywell.com" target="_blank">AeroCPSCommunications@Honeywell.com</a>.</span><br /><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;"><span style="color: black; font-size: 16px; font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><a href=" https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/CGM Singapore_30 day letter translated.pdf" target="_blank">Chinese translated letter</a><br /><a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/641-QIX-912/images/CGM%20Singapore_30 day Checklist 
Translated.pdf" target="_blank">Chinese translated transition checklist</a></span><br /><br />Yours sincerely, </span><br /><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Aileen McDowall </span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Region Vice President AT&amp;R Airlines, EMEAI </span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Honeywell International S&agrave;rl </span><br /><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Brian Davis </span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Region Vice President AT&amp;R Airlines, APAC </span><br /><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">Honeywell Aerospace</span><br /><br style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 16px;" /></div></div>
